---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			main {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 1200px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 40px 20px;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			.hero-section {
				text-align: center;
				margin: 60px 0 80px;
			}
			.hero-section h1 {
				font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
				font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 10vw, 5rem);
				letter-spacing: 0.15em;
				background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff, #d6b25e);
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
				margin: 10px 0;
			}
			.hero-section .mark {
				color: var(--accent-gold);
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				opacity: 0.8;
			}

			/* 响应式祭坛网格 */
			.altar-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
				gap: 25px;
			}

			/* 手机端深度优化：垂直堆叠并增加呼吸感 */
			@media (max-width: 800px) {
				.altar-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
					gap: 20px;
					padding: 0 10px;
				}
				.temple-card {
					padding: 45px 20px !important;
				}
				.hero-section { margin-bottom: 40px; }
			}

			.temple-card {
				position: relative;
				background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(25,25,25,0.9), rgba(10,10,10,1));
				border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
				padding: 60px 30px;
				text-align: center;
				text-decoration: none;
				transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.2, 1, 0.3, 1);
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
			}

			.temple-card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-8px);
				border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
			}

			.temple-card h2 {
				font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
				font-size: 1.6rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.2em;
				margin: 15px 0;
				transition: 0.4s;
			}

			.temple-card p {
				font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
				font-style: italic;
				color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.5;
				max-width: 220px;
			}

			.stud {
				width: 6px; height: 6px;
				transform: rotate(45deg);
				margin-bottom: 10px;
				background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
			}

			/* 手机端特定：取消部分悬停位移避免误触感不佳 */
			@media (hover: none) {
				.temple-card:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
			}

			/* 配色方案 */
			.card-writing:hover h2 { color: #f0ebdc; }
			.card-writing:hover .stud { background: #f0ebdc; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #f0ebdc; }

			.card-gallery:hover h2 { color: #e1e5e9; }
			.card-gallery:hover .stud { background: #e1e5e9; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #e1e5e9; }

			.card-with-you:hover h2 { color: #d2c3a0; }
			.card-with-you:hover .stud { background: #d2c3a0; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #d2c3a0; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="hero-section">
				<span class="mark">✠</span>
				<h1>NEMU · ARCHIVE</h1>
			</section>
			<div class="altar-grid">
				<a href="/writing/essays" class="temple-card card-writing">
					<div class="stud"></div>
					<h2>WRITING</h2>
					<p>“ 在墨痕的间隙，捕捉灵魂碎裂的低语。”</p>
				</a>
				<a href="/gallery" class="temple-card card-gallery">
					<div class="stud"></div>
					<h2>GALLERY</h2>
					<p>“ 光影的残像，是时间在这个世界留下的唯一证词。”</p>
				</a>
				<a href="/with-you" class="temple-card card-with-you">
					<div class="stud"></div>
					<h2>WITH YOU</h2>
					<p>“ 跨越禁忌的边界，于虚无中与你同频。”</p>
				</a>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
